    "best_read": "Catch in the pocket and release in rhythm. With no arrows and a short window, trust the cushion: short closeout means shoot, and shoot now.",
    "acceptable_reads": [
      "Rip and drive baseline if the defender is flying past — still a good shot, but slower than the catch-and-shoot the closeout gave you."
